      "to_id": "cec50b17:33",
      "content": "## Follow-up task (add to your current worktree commit)\n\nAfter you finish the approval button task, also fix the agent card selection styling:\n\n**Problem:** In light theme, the selected agent card is visually reversed (dark background / inverted) instead of highlighted (e.g. a colored border or subtle filled highlight).\n\n**What to fix:** In `public/app.js` and/or `public/index.html` / CSS, find the `.selected` or `.active` style for agent cards. In light theme it should show a highlight (e.g. primary color border or light tinted background), not a full color inversion.\n\nCommit this as a separate commit in the same worktree with message: `fix(ui): highlight selected agent card instead of inverting in light theme`\n\nThen report DONE to me with all commit SHAs.",
